cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with the problem of video moment localization with natural language, which involves both language understanding and visual reasoning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel Temporal Compositional Modular Network (TCMN) that utilizes visual and temporal information, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of modules to measure similarity between segments and descriptions suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
